---
import AboutHeroImage from '../assets/blog-placeholder-about.jpg';
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
import { GITHUB_REPO } from '../consts';
---

<Layout
	title="About"
	description="Embedded firmware benchmarks and agent evaluation for Fieldwork."
	pubDate={new Date('May 17 2026')}
	heroImage={AboutHeroImage}
>
	<p>
		Fieldwork evaluates coding agents on real embedded hardware: STM32 Nucleo boards, XMOS xcore devices,
		and the tasks defined in the <a href={GITHUB_REPO}>fieldwork-firmware</a> repository.
	</p>
	<p>
		Each benchmark bundles a rendered task, runs an agent in a sandboxed toolchain environment, and scores
		the result with platform-specific observers (UART traces, VCD waveforms, monitor plugins, and more).
	</p>
	<p>
		Use this blog for release notes, benchmark methodology, and write-ups on individual tasks and rollouts.
	</p>
</Layout>
